2011-08-26T04:15:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-26/kan-resigns-as-japan-prime-minister-after-backlash-over-handling-of-quake.html
Japanese Prime Minister  Naoto Kan 
told members of the ruling  Democratic Party  he will step down, a
party official said today.  Kan made the announcement at a meeting of senior party
members today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
